            <p class="mf-copy no-bpadding">If a student team takes on the challenge of organizing a community screening, they’ll develop a whole range of critical skills in the process -- creative problem solving, communication, collaboration, critical analysis, and effecting change.
                In an ideal world, your school will give you some sort of recognition or even credit for this work, since the organizing team will learn so much in making this initiative successful.</p>
        </div>
