    <section class="copy-container moving-forward-copy">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <p class="mf-copy no-bpadding">If you get an assignment that involves lots of rote memorization, work with your teacher to transform it to something that will help you develop essential skills. Push hard for unstructured blocks of time each school month to explore areas
                of interest, and lobby for paths to complete independent study initiatives, and get credit for them. Find, or invent, your own after-school or summer job. Check out the organization <a href="http://www.stuvoice.org/" target="_blank">StudentVoice</a>,
